NAME

DateTime::Locale::sbp - Locale data examples for the Sangu (sbp) locale

DESCRIPTION

This pod file contains examples of the locale data available for the Sangu locale.

Date Formats

Full 

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = Jumanne, 5 Mwitope 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = Ijumaa, 22 Muhaano 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = Jumamosi, 15 Munyense -10

Long

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 5 Mwitope 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22 Muhaano 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15 Munyense -10

Medium

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 5 Mwi 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22 Muh 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15 Mye -10

Short

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 05/02/2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22/12/1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15/09/-10

Available Formats

Bh (h B)

   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 9 B
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 4 B
